OL,3,C'Prisoner in her own home' risk for
OL,4,Cdisabled woman as funding falls short
OL,6,FAs her symptoms worsen, she will no
OL,7,Flonger be able to use the stairs -
OL,8,Fmeaning she urgently needs a bedroom
OL,9,Fand wet room on the ground floor.
OL,11,FBut despite a statutory Disabled
OL,12,FFacilities Grant being available, it
OL,13,Fhas been frozen at a #30,000 maximum
OL,14,Ffor more than 15 years. With the
OL,15,Ffamily's required extension estimated
OL,16,Fat #75,000, the gap between what's
OL,17,Favailable and what's needed is growing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
