OL,3,C'Prisoner in her own home' risk for
OL,4,Cdisabled woman as funding falls short
OL,6,FThe Cooks were moved into social
OL,7,Fhousing after they could no longer
OL,8,Fafford private rent. Although their
OL,9,Fcurrent home is the 'best available,'
OL,10,Fit has no accessible bedroom or
OL,11,Fbathroom downstairs, and the stairlift
OL,12,Frecently installed will become
OL,13,Funusable as Charlotte's condition
OL,14,Fdeteriorates.
OL,16,FHer father says without the extension,
OL,17,FCharlotte risks being confined to the
OL,18,Ffirst floor - unable to come
OL,19,Fdownstairs to see her three young
OL,20,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
