OL,3,C'Prisoner in her own home' risk for
OL,4,Cdisabled woman as funding falls short
OL,6,FThat leaves a shortfall of around
OL,7,F#45,000 - and unless the Cooks can
OL,8,Fprove they can cover all remaining
OL,9,Fcosts, the application process for
OL,10,Feven the mandatory grant cannot begin.
OL,12,F"It feels like you're being penalised
OL,13,Fbecause you can't find the money," the
OL,14,Ffamily told ITV News. "The grant is
OL,15,Fnot fit for purpose. It's a long
OL,16,Fprocess and Charlotte doesn't have
OL,17,Ftime on her side - some live 20 years,
OL,18,Fsome just one."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
