OL,3,C'Prisoner in her own home' risk for
OL,4,Cdisabled woman as funding falls short
OL,6,FIn a statement the government said:
OL,7,F"we know adapted homes can have a
OL,8,Ftransformative impact on the lives of
OL,9,Fpeople like Charlotte.
OL,11,F"That's why we've increased the
OL,12,Fdisabled facilities grant to #711m
OL,13,Fthis financial year so we can fund
OL,14,Fthousands of additional home
OL,15,Fadaptations for people with
OL,16,Fdisabilities and life-limiting
OL,17,Fillnesses."
OL,19,FWest Berkshire Council said it is
OL,20,Funable to offer discretionary support
OL,21,Fdue to demand and limited budgets:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
