OL,3,C'Prisoner in her own home' risk for
OL,4,Cdisabled woman as funding falls short
OL,6,F"There is a high volume of applicants
OL,7,Fand we do not currently have the
OL,8,Fbudget to offer discretionary funding.
OL,9,FWe genuinely understand how difficult
OL,10,Fthis situation is and officers
OL,11,Fcontinue to explore whether any
OL,12,Falternative funding routes or
OL,13,Fsolutions may help the applicant."
